column5: Hi All,  Any suggestions for fishing spots in the Toronto area for the weekend? Does not matter what I catch.  Thanks

Toronto Islands is pretty solid right now, but this weekend it will be VERY busy out there - actually anywhere in TO will probably be really busy this weekend. Grenedier pond also holds multiple species.  Throw Toronto fishing into the search engine at the top right and you get some results...
Try everywhere.  Catch whats in season   Eat till you glow
